{"tid":2262239,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大灣區投票倘舞弊 曾國衞拒評廉署冇符  林卓廷質疑靠公安如「夢遊仙境」","createTime":"2020-10-29T02:59:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T08:24:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"90cf0c568009b16a4324a9425a9e4f953124d190","tid":2262239,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T02:59:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201029/EYOIZJBCJZCLVASP2MDKKYZPAE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201029%2FEYOIZJBCJZCLVASP2MDKKYZPAE%2F&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5Kind5d2ehbLCfOFFYxDFDkZk%3D&h=48ff23b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201029%2FEYOIZJBCJZCLVASP2MDKKYZPAE%2F&h=2aca71fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201029/EYOIZJBCJZCLVASP2MDKKYZPAE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n大灣區投票倘舞弊 曾國衞拒評廉署冇符 <br />\n林卓廷質疑靠公安如「夢遊仙境」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dMJpkV_T8VYgQL0JxRMa6HXt8oE=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TKYX4HE3QRBBHFOKI54UABHGXU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdMJpkV_T8VYgQL0JxRMa6HXt8oE%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTKYX4HE3QRBBHFOKI54UABHGXU.jpg&h=47a71864&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曾國衞<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】特區政府勢修例推行大灣區投票，政制及內地事務局長曾國衞表明，局方正與律政司、選舉事務處研究境外投票可行性，但未有計劃更改有關「通常在港居住」的選民資格要求。不過當民主派要求曾國衞交代，廉政公署沒有跨境執法權下，如何調查賄選等舞弊行為，曾未有回應，只稱不同意內地投票必會出現買票、種票，亦未有回應內地法治水平遠低於香港質疑。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨楊岳橋昨早於立法會大會向政制局提質詢，質疑大灣區投票削弱選舉公平性，。。。。。。。。。。。、如何有效運送選票、票箱，以及違反選舉法例的執法工作等因素。另他指局方同時研究為有需要人士作特別投票安排及電子派票等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無計劃更改通常居港要求<br />\n<br />\n曾國衞指截至去年中，通常逗留在廣東省18歲或以上香港居民約有33萬人，至於境外投票涉及選民登記資格問題，曾指未有計劃更改選民須通常居於香港的要求，惟外界質疑目前法例未有明確定義何謂「通常居住」，在大灣區的港人如何符合規定問題上，曾國衞未有任何回應。<br />\n<br />\n如何防止賄選及執法工作亦是推行境外投票的重要問題。民主黨林卓廷質。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n曾國衞反稱不同意內地投票必然出現買票種票，稱會徵詢廉署意見，又指。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n曾國衞多次重申境外投票是社會多年來的訴求，楊岳橋批評港府以民意為由，。。。。。。。。。。。。，「係咪身在外地嘅香港居民意見就唔聽取呢？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/nDFJrF81O_DzO0vORwKmICRcvIQ=/1771x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CDYPH2MGFVFMJK5QZ5XTHDXNGQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FnDFJrF81O_DzO0vORwKmICRcvIQ%3D%2F1771x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCDYPH2MGFVFMJK5QZ5XTHDXNGQ.jpg&h=dbd3dba4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林卓廷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pNmM5HB8QppJcovjHJrSWUmptMo=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PMQWTEZYE5GQPAFTY6HH4CQT74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpNmM5HB8QppJcovjHJrSWUmptMo%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPMQWTEZYE5GQPAFTY6HH4CQT74.jpg&h=bf545731&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n楊岳橋"},{"pid":"9ffdeb4126c5f03947ea02c7190bc87cc4e72183","tid":2262239,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T03:27:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e2cdfd357747e81976b2c94599e873fcf6096f4","tid":2262239,"uid":296830,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T08:22:52.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"large\">政內焗腸曾國衞，名字有個大劣英文譯法叫ZENG, Guowei。佢咁乸擦雜總鞋、咁乸愛国，改名曾愛国吧!</span></strong>"},{"pid":"2ebb4ce384e28894be827a51ebd98759a3212ef6","tid":2262239,"uid":75072,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T08:24:51.000Z","msg":